- backer = @notification.backer
- project = backer.project

|Great news, #{project.user.display_name}! #{link_to backer.user.display_name, user_url(backer.user)} just contributed to your project! 
br
br
|Contribution Amount: 
strong #{backer.display_value}
br
br
|Reward Selected: 
- if backer.reward
  strong #{number_to_currency backer.reward.minimum_value, precision: 0}
  |  &mdash; #{backer.reward.description}
-else
  |  No reward selected. If this was in error, please email #{mail_to Configuration[:email_contact]}
br
br
|Contributor email: #{backer.user.email}
br
br
|You can view all contributors here: #{link_to project_by_slug_url(permalink: project.permalink, anchor: 'backers'), project_by_slug_url(permalink: project.permalink, anchor: 'backers')}
br
br
|And you can send an update to all contributors: #{link_to project_by_slug_url(permalink: project.permalink, anchor: 'updates'), project_by_slug_url(permalink: project.permalink, anchor: 'updates')}
br
br
|Keep on truckin',
br
|The #{Configuration[:company_name]} Team
